high_descs: Turn around and face the sink to your right.
Take the silver knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn left and face the table with the apple on your left.
Slice the apple on the table in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter near the sink on your left.
Place the silver knife on the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the table on your left.
Take an apple slice from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the microwave in front of you.
Heat up the apple slice in front of you in the microwave and take it out.
Face the counter on the right.
Place the warm apple slice on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm apple slice on the counter by the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Turn left then face the left side of the table
Slice the apple
Turn left and head to the counter on the left side of the sink
Put knife on the counter
Turn left head to the table
Pickup a slice of apple
Turn left then head to the microwave
Open the microwave put in and out slice apple
Pick up the slice apple then turn right on the counter
Put the slice apple on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the warm slice apple on the counter

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and step forward to face the kitchen table.
Cut the apple on the kitchen table into slices.
Turn around and step forward to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn around and step forward to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the piece of apple on the kitchen table.
Turn around to face the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Step to the right to face the counter.
Place the piece of apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it on the counter by the microwave.
